  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Category</strong>: Clan<br /><strong>Prerequisite</strong>: Akimichi Clan, Level 8+</p><hr /><p>You have learned to convert your Calories to provide additional benefits. You gain the following Benefits;</p><ul><li><p>Increase your Strength or Constitution score by 1, to a maximum of 20.</p></li><li><p>As a bonus action on your turn, you can spend 5 Calories and 2 Chakra die. When you do, you regain a number of chakra equal to the result of the spent Chakra die + your Constitution ability score. You can do this once per long rest.</p></li><li><p>Akimichi clan Jutsu you cast using Calories, have their calorie cost reduced by 1</p></li></ul>",
